# Spark Sketch - The UI Editor

Real-time code editor for React Native with instant deploy to Aether Engine.

## Features
- Syntax-highlighted code editing (via WebView + Prism.js)
- One-tap Deploy to Aether vault
- Clean / Preview / Deploy actions
- Persistent multi-file project support

## Project Structure
(See folder layout above)

## Quick Start
1. `npm install`
2. `npx expo start`
3. Write code → Hit **🚀 DEPLOY**

## Deployment Bridge
The `deployToAether` function saves your sketch as a project array in `@aether_vault` for Aether Engine to pick up.
